pageContext.claim: “In one Michigan county, using Dominion Voting Systems, nearly 6,000 votes were discovered that were wrongly switched from Trump to Biden. They called it a glitch. You know, a glitch. That's, like, the machine broke.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is talking about a documented case of human error which was quickly caught -- and would have been found during the county canvass process when certifying vote. The machine count was later confirmed by a hand count.
